Raccoons are a serious predator in any rural or suburban area.{{fact}}


==Active deterrents==
* Dogs
* Electric fences

==Passive deterrents==
Hardscaping.  Massive, massive hardscaping.  Tall fences with loose wire tops that flops the raccoons off their climb, deep (2-4 feet) impassable footings to keep them from digging under are not unheard of.